 was appointed peritus by Pope John XXIII, serving as an expert theological advisor to members of the Second Vatican Council until its conclusion in 1965. At 
<REF ID="1552.16" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="subj-det">
<REFEX REG08-TYPE="name" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="nominal" CASE="genitive">Küng's</REFEX>
