</ALT-REFEX>
</REF>
 book Infallible? An Inquiry (1971). Consequently, on December 18, 1979, 
<REF ID="1552.19" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="np-subj">
<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="pronoun" CASE="nominative">he</REFEX>
