</REF>
 retirement (Emeritierung) in 1996. To this day 
<REF ID="1552.23" SEMCAT="person" SYNCAT="np-subj">
<REFEX REG08-TYPE="pronoun" EMPHATIC="no" HEAD="pronoun" CASE="nominative">he</REFEX>
